data.text: @4AnimalLife I didn't get all that. Maybe mine is defective. I just hear Bill Gates talking to me through my molars. At least I get good advice about using Windows now.  🤪

@2huskies4us Thanks! It's so cool to have the jab and so far I feel good, just a tiny bit of soreness on my arm.

Thanks for the heads-up on the electronics. 😉 The fun part is now I can read minds, see the entire ultraviolet spectrum and feel the earth's magnetic field. 😜

@4AnimalLife Yea! So happy for you, Lori!

PS, the Bill Gates chip won't be fully operational till after the 2nd but don't be surprised if your TV changes channels unbidden or microwave starts by itself, it's just test runs. Be careful if Alexa gets grumpy though. (She's jealous.) 🤪
